data.description: Back on the market, The buyers got cold feet! This home appraised at $380,000 which means YOU WILL MAKE $40,000 by purchasing this home! Charming 2-story Liberty Homes in the desirable Stone Creek Ranch community. 2800sf floor plan offers versatile formal dining/living, & fantastic open-concept family room w/soaring vaulted ceilings. Light & bright breakfast space opens to Chef's kitchen, boasting 42" cabinetry, elegant granite counters, & modern SS appliances. 1st floor Primary Suite w/bay windows & spa-like en-suite bath, complete w/dual sinks, spa tub + separate shower & huge walk-in closet. Large game room up, + 4 beds & 2 full baths for sharing. Large covered patio overlooks fenced backyard with NO back neighbors. Approx 1mi to Stone Creek Ranch clubhouse, park, pool, & lake w/walking trails. Near endless premier shopping, dining, entertainment, & major highways 290 & TX-99 for an easy commute.
